{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/css/float-flex/","result":{"data":{"site":{"siteMetadata":{"title":"Jane's PS Blog","author":"[Jisun Lim]","siteUrl":"https://janeljs.github.io","comment":{"disqusShortName":"","utterances":"janeljs/janeljs.github.io"},"sponsor":{"buyMeACoffeeId":"janeljs"}}},"markdownRemark":{"id":"200552ad-7361-568c-a14d-03a18929da4c","excerpt":"float float은 flexbox가 나오기 이전에 항목들을 정렬하는데 사용했었지만, 이제는 flexbox를 통해서 훨씬 더 편하게 웹 페이지를 구성할 수 있다. float left center right flexbox flex flex: HTML 항목들을 수평 또는 수직으로 정렬하는 것을 도움 flexbox axis main axis: 정렬되는 방향이 속하는 축 cross axis: main axis 반대축 (수직<->수평) container에 적용할 수 있는 속성값 display flex…","html":"<h2 id=\"float\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#float\" aria-label=\"float permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>float</h2>\n<p>float은 flexbox가 나오기 이전에 항목들을 정렬하는데 사용했었지만, 이제는 flexbox를 통해서 훨씬 더 편하게 웹 페이지를 구성할 수 있다.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>float</p>\n<ul>\n<li>left</li>\n<li>center</li>\n<li>right</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token comment\">/* 오른쪽으로 contact button 보내기 */</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">contact-btn</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token selector\">#search-bar</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n<span class=\"token property\">float</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> right<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"flexbox\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flexbox\" aria-label=\"flexbox permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flexbox</h1>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>flex</p>\n<ul>\n<li>flex: HTML 항목들을 수평 또는 수직으로 정렬하는 것을 도움</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"flexbox-axis\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#flexbox-axis\" aria-label=\"flexbox axis permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>flexbox axis</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>main axis: 정렬되는 방향이 속하는 축</li>\n<li>cross axis: main axis 반대축 (수직&#x3C;->수평)</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"container에-적용할-수-있는-속성값\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#container%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1%EA%B0%92\" aria-label=\"container에 적용할 수 있는 속성값 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>container에 적용할 수 있는 속성값</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>display</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-direction</p>\n<ul>\n<li>row: default value: left->right</li>\n<li>row-reverse: right->left</li>\n<li>column: top->bottom</li>\n<li>column-reverse: bottom->top</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-wrap</p>\n<ul>\n<li>nowrap: default value: item들이 한 줄에 꽉 참</li>\n<li>wrap: 아이템들이 다음 줄로 넘어감</li>\n<li>wrap-reverse</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token selector\">.parent</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">display</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> flex<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">flex-wrap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> wrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n  <span class=\"token property\">justify-content</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> center<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-flow</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>flex-direction + flex-wrap</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\"><span class=\"token property\">flex-flow</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> column nowrap<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"main-axis에서-item-배치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#main-axis%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-item-%EB%B0%B0%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"main axis에서 item 배치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>main axis에서 item 배치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>justify-content</p>\n<ul>\n<li>flex-start: default value: left->right or top->bottom</li>\n<li>flex-end: right or bottom justified (순서는 그대로)</li>\n<li>center: 가운데 정렬</li>\n<li>space-around</li>\n<li>space-evenly: 같은 간격으로 정렬</li>\n<li>space-between: 맨 왼쪽과 오른쪽은 화면 모서리에 부착하고 가운데 요소들은 같은 간격으로 정렬</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 id=\"cross-axis에서-item-배치\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#cross-axis%EC%97%90%EC%84%9C-item-%EB%B0%B0%EC%B9%98\" aria-label=\"cross axis에서 item 배치 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>cross axis에서 item 배치</h3>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>align-items</p>\n<ul>\n<li>center</li>\n<li>baseline: 텍스트가 baseline에 맞도록 크기가 다른 item들 배치 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>align-content</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"item에-적용할-수-있는-속성값\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#item%EC%97%90-%EC%A0%81%EC%9A%A9%ED%95%A0-%EC%88%98-%EC%9E%88%EB%8A%94-%EC%86%8D%EC%84%B1%EA%B0%92\" aria-label=\"item에 적용할 수 있는 속성값 permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>item에 적용할 수 있는 속성값</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>order</p>\n<ul>\n<li>0: default value: html에 있는 순서</li>\n<li>1,2,3…: 순서 조정 가능</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-grow</p>\n<ul>\n<li>0: default value</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">item 1</code>을 2 <code class=\"language-text\">item 2</code>를 1로 지정해 놓고 화면을 움직이면 2:1의 비율로 늘어난다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-shrink</p>\n<ul>\n<li>0: default value</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">item 1</code>을 2 <code class=\"language-text\">item 2</code>를 1로 지정해 놓고 화면을 움직이면 2:1의 비율로 줄어든다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>flex-basis</p>\n<ul>\n<li>auto: default value</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">item 1</code>을 60% <code class=\"language-text\">item 2</code>를 40%로 지정해 놓으면 창이 커지고 작아질 때 해당 비율로 변한다.</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>align-self</p>\n<ul>\n<li>아이템별로 아이템 정렬 가능</li>\n<li>center</li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 id=\"\" style=\"position:relative;\"><a href=\"#\" aria-label=\" permalink\" class=\"anchor before\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" focusable=\"false\" height=\"16\" version=\"1.1\" viewBox=\"0 0 16 16\" width=\"16\"><path fill-rule=\"evenodd\" d=\"M4 9h1v1H4c-1.5 0-3-1.69-3-3.5S2.55 3 4 3h4c1.45 0 3 1.69 3 3.5 0 1.41-.91 2.72-2 3.25V8.59c.58-.45 1-1.27 1-2.09C10 5.22 8.98 4 8 4H4c-.98 0-2 1.22-2 2.5S3 9 4 9zm9-3h-1v1h1c1 0 2 1.22 2 2.5S13.98 12 13 12H9c-.98 0-2-1.22-2-2.5 0-.83.42-1.64 1-2.09V6.25c-1.09.53-2 1.84-2 3.25C6 11.31 7.55 13 9 13h4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a></h1>\n<p><strong><em>Source</em></strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>studio mar css</li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.codecademy.com/learn/make-a-website\">codeacademy</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/display\">MDN display</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7neASrWEFEM&#x26;feature=emb_logo\">드림코딩 by 엘리</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/a-guide-to-flexbox/\">complete guide to flexbox</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://flexboxfroggy.com/#ko\">flexbox practice froggy</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"[css] CSS의 꽃 flexbox 사용하는 법(feat. float bye bye~)","date":"November 12, 2020"}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/css/float-flex/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/html/emmet/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[html] html 태그를 빠른 시간 안에 작성하는 법(feat. Emmet)","category":"html","draft":false}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/css/block-inline/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"[css] Inline, Block, Inline-block 비교","category":"css","draft":false}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3128451518","3260639066"]}